name: THE ANTI-NFT JOKE
description:

HAS IT MADE YOUR LIFE ANY BETTER?

NOT EVERYTHING HAS TO BE CRYPTO, ASSHOLE.

ARTISTS HAVE BEEN MAKING MONEY ONLINE FOR DECADES
WITHOUT THE FUCKING BLOCKCHAIN AND WASTING A MONTH´S
WORTH OF ENERGY WITH A SINGLE CLICK, THEY DIDN'T

JUST ADMIT THAT YOU CARE MORE ABOUT CRYPTO AND/OR
MAKING BANK ON A FAD RATHER THAN THE LIVELIHOODS OF
ACTUAL ARTISTS.
